NAME
	user-popper - batch create users

SYNOPSIS
	user-popper [OPTION]
	
DESCRIPTION
	Creates users from a text file list and assign them to groups, based on the expiring date of their labor contracts.
	
	--create
		create users and assign them to specific groups. For safety purposes, this program creates dedicated skeleton files, allocated in /etc directory
	
	--remove
		removes users and dedicated skeleton files
		
	--help
		display this help and exit
		
AUTHOR
	Written by Joao Ricardo de Souza Gomes. April 2022.